# Release and Changelog Policy — `actions`

Follow the branch-aware policy in `senior-coding-actions`:
[.cursor/skills/senior-coding-actions/SKILL.md](mdc:.cursor/skills/senior-coding-actions/SKILL.md)

## Required behavior

- On `release/*` or `hotfix/*`: update `package.json` version and matching top version section in `CHANGELOG.md`.
- On other branches: do not change `package.json` version; add one-line changelog entry under `## [Unreleased]`.
- Every changelog item must be exactly one line (single concise sentence).
- Iterative in-scope improvements of the same implementation must not create extra changelog lines; keep or update one line for the final delivered scope.
- Do not finish with missing or inconsistent changelog/version updates.
- Write changelog entries in English only.
